                         Privacy and Security Notice

                    2002 ARM Program Science Team Meeting
                             April 8 - 12, 2002
                  Hilton Hotel in St. Petersburg, Florida.

                                              [stpete.jpg]
                               Surrounding area of St. Petersburg, Florida

     * Register for Meeting  Register now for the 2002 ARM Science Team
       Meeting to be held April 8-12, 2002, in St. Petersburg, Florida, at
       the Hilton Hotel.
     * [update.gif] ARM Store Shop for ARM Gear directly from our website.
       To save shipping costs, ask to have your purchases delivered during
       the ARM Science Team Meeting.
     * [update.gif] The deadline has passed for submitting poster
       presentations. If you have any questions, please contact Nancy
       Burleigh at 509-375-2785.
     * Poster Board Information The poster boards are 4 ft x 8 ft with a
       1-inch frame. Each presenter is allotted half a board, so that
       makes 46-inches high x 47-inches wide available for each poster.
       Push pins and removable plastic adhesive are the only medium that
       will be accepted for hanging posters. Push pins will be provided at
       the Science Team Meeting for your convenience.
     * View submitted poster abstracts sorted by Author or Title for the
       2002 Science Team Meeting. For abstracts and proceedings from past
       meetings, check the ARM Program Conference Proceedings web page.
     * Instructions for submitting extended abstracts. The extended
       abstracts (one to four pages) are due at the time of the Science
       Team Meeting.
